{"content": "<h2>Open Call for Punks with Lore</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>We are looking for the top 69 Punks with lore. A story that is so memorable, hilarious or downright eye watering...that it must be memorialised on The Line. The owner of punk is not as important as the lore... so the applications will be judged on the merit of the lore not the rarity and notoriety of the holder...although the two often overlap.</p><p>Punk Lore might be something personal to how you ended up with your punk... it may be something the punk was featured in... it could be something that happened to your punk. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>The Burnt Punk Lore</h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"754\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-1017x1024.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-1017x1024.png 1017w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-298x300.png 298w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-150x150.png 150w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-768x773.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-600x604.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM-100x100.png 100w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.30.16 PM.png 1128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>CryptoPunk #2317 was burned by ROBNESS on July 13th 2021</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>ROBNESS acquired Punk #2317 on July 12th 2021 for 18.9 eth. 24 hours later the punk was 'burnt' by sending it to the Ethereum burn address. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"337\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-1024x461.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-1024x461.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-300x135.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-768x346.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-1536x691.png 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-2048x922.png 2048w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-1320x594.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-26-at-12.43.34 PM-600x270.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Share Your Punk Lore</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Add your lore to the form below or <a href=\"https://x.com/mintfaced\">tweet @mintfaced</a>. The top 69 stories will be added to The Line along with the corresponding punk.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line1000?coords=28.24x12.16x-14.05x1.04\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCryptopunks | Line 1000\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tExit via The Line Gift Shop\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}